 In Angular testing-attribute-directives in app/shared/highlight.directive.spec.ts (selected tests) in this part of code is wrong.
url: https://angular.io/guide/testing-attribute-directives

 // dispatch a DOM event so that Angular responds to the input value change.
  input.value = 'green';
  input.dispatchEvent(newEvent('input'));
  fixture.detectChanges();

Should be  input.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));  and not  input.dispatchEvent(newEvent('input'));

